00:13:24.120 --> 00:13:26.260
ili mucaju, koji su mi pričali što im se

00:13:26.260 --> 00:13:27.600
rješava u životu,

00:13:28.200 --> 00:13:30.480
dao bi im samo neki mali hint u kojem smjeru

00:13:30.480 --> 00:13:31.180
da pokušaju

00:13:31.180 --> 00:13:34.460
i dobio sam nekoliko

00:13:34.460 --> 00:13:36.420
pozadinskih

00:13:36.420 --> 00:13:38.140
feedbackova da

00:13:38.140 --> 00:13:39.940
ajmo reći da je uspjelo

00:13:39.940 --> 00:13:42.020
ili da su radili na tome i uspjeli su

00:13:42.020 --> 00:13:44.040
napraviti neki taj veliki task

00:13:44.040 --> 00:13:46.260
zahvaljujući tome što su

00:13:46.260 --> 00:13:48.180
uvek šili da, malo su pogledali u sebe.

00:13:48.700 --> 00:13:50.900
Da li si

00:13:50.900 --> 00:13:52.300
radio sa

00:13:52.300 --> 00:13:54.680
nekim, tko ti je bio

00:13:54.680 --> 00:13:56.380
podrškar, recimo s nekom

00:13:56.380 --> 00:13:58.660
profesionalcem ili si to

00:13:58.660 --> 00:13:59.800
jednostavno

00:13:59.800 --> 00:14:02.240
već u mlađoj dobi, ne znam

00:14:02.240 --> 00:14:04.700
tineđerskoj ili kasnijim 20-im

00:14:04.700 --> 00:14:05.220
godinama

00:14:05.220 --> 00:14:08.440
samostalno rješavao te probleme?

00:14:08.800 --> 00:14:10.820
Mislim, ne bi se sad predugo zadržavao

00:14:10.820 --> 00:14:11.940
na ovoj tematici, ali

00:14:11.940 --> 00:14:14.660
me zanima kakav ti je bio ono modus operandi?

00:14:14.800 --> 00:14:15.960
Kako si došao do toga?

00:14:15.960 --> 00:14:18.160
Neki ti idu na govorne vježbe,

00:14:18.700 --> 00:14:19.620
nikad na govorne vježbe.

00:14:19.740 --> 00:14:22.300
Neki ti idu na te govorne vježbe gdje ti zapravo

00:14:22.300 --> 00:14:23.780
sebe na neki način demfaš,

00:14:24.620 --> 00:14:26.100
kuliraš u situacijama

00:14:26.100 --> 00:14:28.580
ili

00:14:28.580 --> 00:14:30.120
nađeš neke zajemenske riječi,

00:14:30.260 --> 00:14:31.460
pa nešto pričaš zajemenski.

00:14:32.120 --> 00:14:33.320
Gledam, to nije dugoročno

00:14:33.320 --> 00:14:36.680
solucija, zato što to je nešto

00:14:36.680 --> 00:14:38.400
što ti možeš sad u ovom

00:14:38.400 --> 00:14:39.720
trenu napraviti privremeno.

00:14:40.480 --> 00:14:42.220
Ali nešto dugoročno, ti actually

00:14:42.220 --> 00:14:44.480
moraš baš pogledati u sebe

00:14:44.480 --> 00:14:46.900
i naravno to ne možeš sam.

00:14:47.860 --> 00:14:48.680
Za mene je to

00:14:48.700 --> 00:14:49.640
bio jedan

00:14:49.640 --> 00:14:52.080
majstor

00:14:52.080 --> 00:14:53.900
s kojim sam radio,

00:14:54.560 --> 00:14:56.380
koji me je naučio kako

00:14:56.380 --> 00:14:58.580
zapravo meditirat i kako

00:14:58.580 --> 00:15:00.640
kroz tu meditaciju pomoć sebi

00:15:00.640 --> 00:15:02.540
i ne znam, eventualno

00:15:02.540 --> 00:15:04.380
pomoć drugima, ali prvenstveno zapravo ja sam

00:15:04.380 --> 00:15:05.840
išao tu da pomoglim sebi.

00:15:05.940 --> 00:15:08.280
To je nekaj bio tvoj Mr. Miyagi.

00:15:09.660 --> 00:15:10.400
Tako nešto.

00:15:13.080 --> 00:15:14.380
Kako to izgleda danas

00:15:14.380 --> 00:15:16.700
u tvom životu? Da li imaš nekakve

00:15:17.860 --> 00:15:18.340
ono

00:15:18.340 --> 00:15:19.680
standardne rutine koje se možda

00:15:19.680 --> 00:15:21.680
nastavljaju na ovu

00:15:21.680 --> 00:15:24.260
meditaciju? Da li danas meditaciju

00:15:24.260 --> 00:15:25.860
prakticiraš i imaš još nekakvih

00:15:25.860 --> 00:15:27.980
alata recimo u svom arsenalu

00:15:27.980 --> 00:15:28.720
koji koristiš?

00:15:29.380 --> 00:15:32.160
Pa, mislim sad, neko vrijeme

00:15:32.160 --> 00:15:33.840
nisam meditirao i onda

00:15:33.840 --> 00:15:35.920
taman skužiš

00:15:35.920 --> 00:15:38.120
kao neke stvari

00:15:38.120 --> 00:15:39.960
kao, znaš ono,

00:15:40.160 --> 00:15:42.180
skužiš samo da nešto nešto ima.

00:15:43.040 --> 00:15:43.540
Malo si

00:15:43.540 --> 00:15:45.800
ono, tipa, disbalansiran.

00:15:45.800 --> 00:15:49.000
Neke stvari te krenu

00:15:49.000 --> 00:15:51.080
malo nervirat.

00:15:51.360 --> 00:15:52.720
Neke stvari te krenu, ono,

00:15:52.900 --> 00:15:53.600
živcirat

00:15:53.600 --> 00:15:56.920
na poslu ili nešto. Znaš, ono, vidiš nešto

00:15:56.920 --> 00:15:58.800
pa ti je nešto kao samo onak dobivaš

00:15:58.800 --> 00:16:00.440
neku potrebu da reagiraš

00:16:00.440 --> 00:16:02.540
a nije na tebi da reagiraš.

00:16:03.140 --> 00:16:04.740
I onda zapravo, ono,

00:16:04.880 --> 00:16:06.920
ga shvatim, aha, okej, zato što nisam

00:16:06.920 --> 00:16:07.880
meditirao mjesec dana.

00:16:09.020 --> 00:16:10.960
Pa sam se spustio na tu razinu niskih

00:16:10.960 --> 00:16:12.460
frekvencija gdje ti

00:16:12.460 --> 00:16:15.040
si dopustiš da, ono, zapravo

00:16:15.040 --> 00:16:15.840
na neke stvari

00:16:15.840 --> 00:16:18.860
reagiraš zapravo

00:16:18.860 --> 00:16:21.020
kako bi

00:16:21.020 --> 00:16:22.820
većina odreagirala. A to je, ne znam,

00:16:23.100 --> 00:16:25.220
trubic u autu

00:16:25.220 --> 00:16:26.780
umjesto da, znaš, ono,

00:16:27.080 --> 00:16:28.980
propustiš to i shvatiš, ono, okej, dobro.

00:16:30.420 --> 00:16:30.840
Što je zapravo

00:16:30.840 --> 00:16:31.960
pojnt montaže,

00:16:32.080 --> 00:16:34.840
ovog meditacije? Da ti

00:16:34.840 --> 00:16:36.280
kad, ono,

00:16:36.840 --> 00:16:38.780
si, ajmo reći,

00:16:38.780 --> 00:16:41.180
svjesna svega što se dešava oko tebe,

00:16:41.940 --> 00:16:42.880
kad si svjesna da

00:16:42.880 --> 00:16:44.880
osoba preko puta tebe s kojom

00:16:44.880 --> 00:16:46.720
pričaš, ili si na telefonu,

00:16:46.840 --> 00:16:48.860
ili se mailaš, da i ona

00:16:48.860 --> 00:16:49.760
proživljava nešto.

00:16:50.900 --> 00:16:52.500
Recimo u produkciji je to dosta bitno.

00:16:53.400 --> 00:16:54.740
Znači, nije samo

00:16:54.740 --> 00:16:56.840
stvar biti nekakav bić

00:16:56.840 --> 00:16:58.560
i gurat nešto naprijed

00:16:58.560 --> 00:17:01.200
po cvaku cijenu, pa će nešto biti.

00:17:01.460 --> 00:17:02.920
Ne, trebaš zapravo uzeti u obzir

00:17:02.920 --> 00:17:04.820
da svi ti koji su uključeni

00:17:04.820 --> 00:17:07.220
u taj neki

00:17:07.220 --> 00:17:08.660
proizvod, u to nešto što se

00:17:08.660 --> 00:17:10.760
producirate trenutno, nešto proživljavaju

00:17:10.760 --> 00:17:11.760
u tom trenu drugo.

00:17:12.820 --> 00:17:14.680
Tako da, trebaš naći

00:17:14.880 --> 00:17:16.760
bolji način kako ćeš voditi

00:17:16.760 --> 00:17:18.320
taj cijeli tim

00:17:18.320 --> 00:17:20.980
i kako ćeš ih actually čuti.

00:17:22.040 --> 00:17:23.020
Znači, ljudi nekad se

00:17:23.020 --> 00:17:24.840
prave kod da te čuju,

00:17:25.060 --> 00:17:26.980
kod da te razumiju. Ljudi nekad pričaju

00:17:26.980 --> 00:17:28.960
ukujuš istim jezikom, a ne razumiju se.

00:17:29.560 --> 00:17:31.300
Pričaju onakiste stvari, ne razumiju se.

00:17:31.860 --> 00:17:33.100
Dakle, zapravo, taj

00:17:33.100 --> 00:17:35.100
princip rada,

00:17:35.420 --> 00:17:36.220
ne samo da

00:17:36.220 --> 00:17:39.060
primjenjuju na sebi, znači ono kao na

00:17:39.060 --> 00:17:41.180
na higijeni, to je koje sam

00:17:41.180 --> 00:17:43.180
vam spomenuo, nego zapravo i u produkciji

00:17:43.180 --> 00:17:44.860
svoje i ovoga

00:17:44.880 --> 00:17:46.820
nekako volim, i to fakat je tako,

00:17:46.880 --> 00:17:48.740
to smo onako usvojili kao neku

00:17:48.740 --> 00:17:50.240
metodu rada,

00:17:51.020 --> 00:17:53.140
da imamo jako puno razmijevanja za druge,

00:17:53.360 --> 00:17:54.300
želimo čuti ljude,

00:17:55.700 --> 00:17:57.160
ne guramo, kuđiš ono,

00:17:57.440 --> 00:17:59.300
previše niš svoje, ako ne moramo,

00:17:59.420 --> 00:18:01.200
nekad fakat nemaš izbora, pa moraš,

00:18:02.220 --> 00:18:03.020
ali zapravo

00:18:03.020 --> 00:18:04.460
želimo da to sve

00:18:04.460 --> 00:18:06.960
na kraju kad napravimo proizvod, da to bude

00:18:06.960 --> 00:18:08.180
proizvod jedne zajednice,

00:18:09.200 --> 00:18:11.160
što se kuži. Kuži se ta razlika

00:18:11.160 --> 00:18:12.740
kad je investirana

00:18:12.740 --> 00:18:14.240
energia tih ljudi,

00:18:14.880 --> 00:18:17.320
svojevoljno, a kuži se

00:18:17.320 --> 00:18:19.080
kad je ta energia

00:18:19.080 --> 00:18:22.320
dana,

00:18:22.700 --> 00:18:25.100
kada kažu na kijelu, kradena,

00:18:25.760 --> 00:18:26.920
jer je neko nekom držao gan

00:18:26.920 --> 00:18:29.260
pored lave da to radi za tebe.

00:18:30.500 --> 00:18:33.040
Kad govoriš zapravo da si kroz meditaciju

00:18:33.040 --> 00:18:34.860
da si dobio sposobnost bolje čuti

00:18:34.860 --> 00:18:36.660
drugu osobu, da si dobio očito

00:18:36.660 --> 00:18:38.440
sposobnost bolje empatije,

00:18:40.440 --> 00:18:41.120
i spomenio si

00:18:41.120 --> 00:18:43.160
sad da onda produkt

00:18:43.160 --> 00:18:44.860
recimo nekakvog projekta koji je radio,

00:18:44.880 --> 00:18:46.880
kojim si ti radiš,

00:18:46.880 --> 00:18:48.880
kojim si ti na čelu recimo,

00:18:50.880 --> 00:18:52.880
je bolji proizvod

00:18:54.880 --> 00:18:56.880
iz razloga što ljudi koji su

00:18:56.880 --> 00:18:58.880
dio tima

00:18:58.880 --> 00:19:00.880
projekta, plus ljudi koji su

00:19:00.880 --> 00:19:02.880
recimo dulom zemlje kad si snimao,

00:19:02.880 --> 00:19:04.880
kad ste to radili,

00:19:04.880 --> 00:19:06.880
imali ste i aktere

00:19:06.880 --> 00:19:08.880
koji nisu dio tima,

00:19:08.880 --> 00:19:10.880
jel tako? Ali ako sam te dobro

00:19:10.880 --> 00:19:12.880
ishvatio, rekao si da kad imaš te sposobnosti,

00:19:12.880 --> 00:19:14.880
recimo tu vještinu nekakvu,

00:19:14.880 --> 00:19:16.880
koju si gradio,

00:19:16.880 --> 00:19:18.880
koja je izražena,

00:19:18.880 --> 00:19:20.880
imaš mogućnost stvoriti cijelu

00:19:20.880 --> 00:19:22.880
povezaniju

00:19:22.880 --> 00:19:24.880
i sinergiju zapravo

00:19:24.880 --> 00:19:26.880
između svih članova

00:19:26.880 --> 00:19:28.880
na tom projektu, ne samo

00:19:28.880 --> 00:19:30.880
unutar svog tima.

00:19:30.880 --> 00:19:32.880
Mislim da, ne znam koliko je sad onako to van

00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:34.880
izašlo kad sam pričao

00:19:34.880 --> 00:19:36.880
kako si to shvatio,

00:19:36.880 --> 00:19:38.880
ali doslovno to se može samo svesti

00:19:38.880 --> 00:19:40.880
na ono, simple stvar.

00:19:40.880 --> 00:19:42.880
Just be human.

00:19:42.880 --> 00:19:44.880
Jer ti kad

00:19:44.880 --> 00:19:46.880
nekom, recimo Dulm zemlje

00:19:46.880 --> 00:19:48.880
je kompleksan projekt,

00:19:48.880 --> 00:19:50.880
ti dolaziš ljudima

00:19:50.880 --> 00:19:52.880
u njihov

00:19:52.880 --> 00:19:54.880
living space

00:19:54.880 --> 00:19:56.880
i ti provodiš tamo

00:19:56.880 --> 00:19:58.880
između 7-8 do 10 dana

00:19:58.880 --> 00:20:00.880
i mi s njima tamo nešto stvaramo.

00:20:00.880 --> 00:20:02.880
I mi ne možemo

00:20:02.880 --> 00:20:04.880
tu doći

00:20:04.880 --> 00:20:06.880
kao šišmis iz pakla

00:20:06.880 --> 00:20:08.880
koji tu sad nešto sad će

00:20:08.880 --> 00:20:10.880
ili da nam se ne da

00:20:10.880 --> 00:20:12.880
ili da nešto, znači ono, da šutamo

00:20:12.880 --> 00:20:14.880
tablove po

00:20:14.880 --> 00:20:16.880
setu i tako, znači svaki detalj

00:20:16.880 --> 00:20:18.880
prisutnosti tvoje

00:20:18.880 --> 00:20:20.880
odnosno naše tamo kao tima

00:20:20.880 --> 00:20:22.880
je bitan.

00:20:22.880 --> 00:20:24.880
I zato ja ne

00:20:24.880 --> 00:20:26.880
želim da nas vozi

00:20:26.880 --> 00:20:28.880
vozač koji hračka,

00:20:28.880 --> 00:20:30.880
zato ne ogovolim

00:20:30.880 --> 00:20:32.880
da je tonac koji

00:20:32.880 --> 00:20:34.880
previše puši i ne znam šta priča

00:20:34.880 --> 00:20:36.880
gluposti koje ovoga nikako ne zanimaju.

00:20:36.880 --> 00:20:38.880
Sad baš karikiram, ono.

00:20:38.880 --> 00:20:40.880
Ili da su, ne znam ono, snimatelji

00:20:40.880 --> 00:20:42.880
takvi i takvi ili da

00:20:42.880 --> 00:20:44.880
znači ono, da netko u timu

00:20:44.880 --> 00:20:46.880
pokazuje da zapravo tu

00:20:46.880 --> 00:20:48.880
ne želi bit. I koliko

00:20:48.880 --> 00:20:50.880
god to zvučalo

00:20:50.880 --> 00:20:52.880
kao ono

00:20:52.880 --> 00:20:54.880
bonton, kao pa da, to je normalno

00:20:54.880 --> 00:20:56.880
kao, pa kad nismo svi takvi na setu

00:20:56.880 --> 00:20:58.880
ne, kao

00:20:58.880 --> 00:21:00.880
naprosto koliko god

00:21:00.880 --> 00:21:02.880
ono zvučalo kao pa da, to tak treba bit

00:21:02.880 --> 00:21:04.880
zapravo to tak nije.

00:21:04.880 --> 00:21:06.880
Psihološi gledano

00:21:06.880 --> 00:21:08.880
nakon provedenog nekog

00:21:08.880 --> 00:21:10.880
perioda vremena na setu

00:21:10.880 --> 00:21:12.880
zajedno s ljudima

00:21:12.880 --> 00:21:14.880
ti nakon, ti možeš držati svoj

00:21:14.880 --> 00:21:16.880
coolness dva, tri, četiri

00:21:16.880 --> 00:21:18.880
dana, peti dan ti već pucaš.

00:21:18.880 --> 00:21:20.880
Jer si na istoj lokaciji

00:21:20.880 --> 00:21:22.880
s istim ljudima, može

00:21:22.880 --> 00:21:24.880
ti nije dobro, može ti hrana nije

00:21:24.880 --> 00:21:26.880
dobra, znači sad pričamo o negdje

00:21:26.880 --> 00:21:28.880
smo u Hrvatskoj, znači nismo doma, ne spavamo

00:21:28.880 --> 00:21:30.880
doma nego spavamo po hotelima

00:21:30.880 --> 00:21:32.880
po nekim smještajima i tako dalje

00:21:32.880 --> 00:21:34.880
i to ti je pravi

00:21:34.880 --> 00:21:36.880
test za kru.

00:21:36.880 --> 00:21:38.880
Tu ti kru zapravo pada. Jedno tu

00:21:38.880 --> 00:21:40.880
skužimo ko je dio nas,

00:21:40.880 --> 00:21:42.880
a ko nije dio nas.

00:21:42.880 --> 00:21:44.880
I to se dosta

00:21:44.880 --> 00:21:46.880
brzo iskristalizira. Tu zapravo

00:21:46.880 --> 00:21:48.880
skužiš ko zapravo dijeli tu neku našu

00:21:48.880 --> 00:21:50.880
filozofiju, a ko je

00:21:50.880 --> 00:21:52.880
naprosto nije za to.

00:21:52.880 --> 00:21:54.880
Možda i za neke druge stvari.

00:21:54.880 --> 00:21:56.880
Znači ono za nešto što je malo više

00:21:56.880 --> 00:21:58.880
jednokratno, ono kao

00:21:58.880 --> 00:22:00.880
jednokratno, par dana, dva dana

00:22:00.880 --> 00:22:02.880
snimanja pa to će izdržati.

00:22:02.880 --> 00:22:04.880
Ali ti kad, kažem kad

00:22:04.880 --> 00:22:06.880
prođeš kroz taj prag ljudima

00:22:06.880 --> 00:22:08.880
sad bih pričao za dulom zemlje

00:22:08.880 --> 00:22:10.880
ili neke ideje uspona o

00:22:10.880 --> 00:22:12.880
serije koje se baš ono dulje snimaju.

00:22:12.880 --> 00:22:14.880
Ti na tom pragu

00:22:14.880 --> 00:22:16.880
trebaš zapravo prva stvar

00:22:16.880 --> 00:22:18.880
kao vampiri

00:22:18.880 --> 00:22:20.880
ono znaš moraju te pozvati unutra

00:22:20.880 --> 00:22:22.880
da uđeš. I onda kad

00:22:22.880 --> 00:22:24.880
te puste jednom unutra ti si zapravo tu

00:22:24.880 --> 00:22:26.880
znaš u njihovom

00:22:26.880 --> 00:22:28.880
nejakom domu. To trebaš ovdje

00:22:28.880 --> 00:22:30.880
respektirati. Znači ono

00:22:30.880 --> 00:22:32.880
od pravila kak ćeš stavit čašu

00:22:32.880 --> 00:22:34.880
na stol, da li ćeš ono stavit

00:22:34.880 --> 00:22:36.880
podložak

00:22:36.880 --> 00:22:38.880
ispod čaše vode ili ćeš

00:22:38.880 --> 00:22:40.880
samo stavit na puno drvo.

00:22:40.880 --> 00:22:42.880
Ovoga čašu, to se sve gleda.

00:22:42.880 --> 00:22:44.880
A to ja zapravo isto

00:22:44.880 --> 00:22:46.880
gledam jer sam, mislim,

00:22:46.880 --> 00:22:48.880
ne želim zvučat ko nekakav

00:22:48.880 --> 00:22:50.880
turbo frik sad koji kužiš pazi

00:22:50.880 --> 00:22:52.880
na te sve stvari pa će onda nekom to kasnije

00:22:52.880 --> 00:22:54.880
čitat. Ne, nego

00:22:54.880 --> 00:22:56.880
radi se o bom tonu

00:22:56.880 --> 00:22:58.880
tima ljudi koji dolazi, koji

00:22:58.880 --> 00:23:00.880
radi nešto kvalitetno,

00:23:00.880 --> 00:23:02.880
a za to kvalitetno ima puno više faktora

00:23:02.880 --> 00:23:04.880
od samo snimi to lijepo.

00:23:04.880 --> 00:23:06.880
Da, zapravo

00:23:06.880 --> 00:23:08.880
bez obzira na to što je možda

00:23:08.880 --> 00:23:10.880
nemoguće kontrolirati svaki najmanji detalj,

00:23:10.880 --> 00:23:12.880
jel si svjesan da taj svaki najmanji detalj

00:23:12.880 --> 00:23:14.880
je bitan za finalni

00:23:14.880 --> 00:23:16.880
produkt

00:23:16.880 --> 00:23:18.880
onoga što radite?

00:23:18.880 --> 00:23:20.880
Svoriti se, da kažem,

00:23:20.880 --> 00:23:22.880
kao najbitnija

00:23:22.880 --> 00:23:24.880
stvar koja

00:23:24.880 --> 00:23:26.880
nikako zapravo

00:23:26.880 --> 00:23:28.880
ono da

00:23:28.880 --> 00:23:30.880
skužim kak to drugi ne kuže.

00:23:30.880 --> 00:23:32.880
Ti

00:23:32.880 --> 00:23:34.880
kad si producent recimo

00:23:34.880 --> 00:23:36.880
neke reklame,

00:23:36.880 --> 00:23:38.880
što mi radimo sad dosta u produkciji

00:23:38.880 --> 00:23:40.880
moj, ovoga

00:23:40.880 --> 00:23:42.880
More Magnets,

00:23:42.880 --> 00:23:44.880
jel?

00:23:44.880 --> 00:23:46.880
Kako si rekao, prosti?

00:23:46.880 --> 00:23:48.880
More Magnets.

00:23:50.880 --> 00:23:52.880
Mi imamo neko pravilo da

00:23:52.880 --> 00:23:54.880
svakoj osobi na setu

00:23:54.880 --> 00:23:56.880
znamo ime.

00:23:56.880 --> 00:23:58.880
Znači, kogod

00:23:58.880 --> 00:24:00.880
dolazi, bio od cateringa, bio

00:24:00.880 --> 00:24:02.880
od ekipe iz

00:24:02.880 --> 00:24:04.880
Lighta, Grip-a, kogod,

00:24:04.880 --> 00:24:06.880
znači mi koji smo

00:24:06.880 --> 00:24:08.880
gore na vrhu, ja želim

00:24:08.880 --> 00:24:10.880
znati tko dolazi na set.

00:24:10.880 --> 00:24:12.880
I tako da kad na setu

00:24:12.880 --> 00:24:14.880
ono, ga zovem i kažem njegovo

00:24:14.880 --> 00:24:16.880
ime,

00:24:16.880 --> 00:24:18.880
znam s kim pričam, jel?

00:24:18.880 --> 00:24:20.880
I onda zapravo tu opet, to je opet

00:24:20.880 --> 00:24:22.880
ta neka higijena kužiš odnosa,

00:24:22.880 --> 00:24:24.880
ne ono, kad

00:24:24.880 --> 00:24:26.880
se poznajemo, jer

00:24:26.880 --> 00:24:28.880
često puta će ti doć netko

00:24:28.880 --> 00:24:30.880
čije ime ti ne znaš, bit će neko novi, pa će

00:24:30.880 --> 00:24:32.880
se tamo poznat, vidit ćeš kako

00:24:32.880 --> 00:24:34.880
radi, najčešće se ovoga

00:24:34.880 --> 00:24:36.880
ljudi super uklope i funkaju

00:24:36.880 --> 00:24:38.880
ono, baš dobro,

00:24:38.880 --> 00:24:40.880
jel? Ali nekad se desi

00:24:40.880 --> 00:24:42.880
da dođe ekipa koja naprosto

00:24:42.880 --> 00:24:44.880
iz nekog meja i nepoznatog

00:24:44.880 --> 00:24:46.880
razloga se ne uklope.

00:24:46.880 --> 00:24:48.880
Možda su navikli previše na

00:24:48.880 --> 00:24:50.880
rad kod nekog drugog

00:24:50.880 --> 00:24:52.880
i tamo su navikli da se neko cijelo vrijeme

00:24:52.880 --> 00:24:54.880
dere na njih, da cijelo vrijeme ih neko

00:24:54.880 --> 00:24:56.880
sa čizmom stisne na glavu,

00:24:56.880 --> 00:24:58.880
što isto

00:24:58.880 --> 00:25:00.880
producira neke rezultate,

00:25:00.880 --> 00:25:02.880
ali to nije način na koji ja želim da mi

00:25:02.880 --> 00:25:04.880
produciramo ovog

00:25:04.880 --> 00:25:06.880
rezultate. Pošto je limit do kojeg

00:25:06.880 --> 00:25:08.880
možeš tiskati limun,

00:25:08.880 --> 00:25:10.880
jer nakon toga više ne ide ništa.

00:25:10.880 --> 00:25:12.880
Kako si

00:25:12.880 --> 00:25:14.880
ovo dobro rekao.

00:25:14.880 --> 00:25:16.880
Nekako se mogu i povezati s tim.

00:25:16.880 --> 00:25:18.880
Mislim,

00:25:18.880 --> 00:25:20.880
fantastično mi je ovo što si rekao. Koliko god

00:25:20.880 --> 00:25:22.880
zvučalo jednostavno, to je

00:25:22.880 --> 00:25:24.880
dosta teško i meni koji se trudim

00:25:24.880 --> 00:25:26.880
primijeniti

00:25:26.880 --> 00:25:28.880
u svakodnevnici.

00:25:28.880 --> 00:25:30.880
Just be human, tako si rekao.

00:25:30.880 --> 00:25:32.880
Šta ti to

00:25:32.880 --> 00:25:34.880
točno, osim ovih prekrasnih primjera koji si

00:25:34.880 --> 00:25:36.880
naveo, šta bi ti to još

00:25:36.880 --> 00:25:38.880
moglo označiti?

00:25:38.880 --> 00:25:40.880
Mislim da zapravo

00:25:40.880 --> 00:25:42.880
što je

00:25:42.880 --> 00:25:44.880
čovjek?

00:25:44.880 --> 00:25:46.880
Kako to

00:25:46.880 --> 00:25:48.880
definirati? Znači, da li mi

00:25:48.880 --> 00:25:50.880
živimo u nekoj zajednici, da li živimo

00:25:50.880 --> 00:25:52.880
u nekom društvu? Ja ne gledam

00:25:52.880 --> 00:25:54.880
ljude po tome

00:25:54.880 --> 00:25:56.880
za koga navijaju,

00:25:56.880 --> 00:25:58.880
što slušaju,

00:25:58.880 --> 00:26:00.880
naravno da imam neke svoje

00:26:00.880 --> 00:26:02.880
preference oko toga,

00:26:02.880 --> 00:26:04.880
ali ti ne možeš nekom to gurati

00:26:04.880 --> 00:26:06.880
i

00:26:06.880 --> 00:26:08.880
tvrditi da je tvoje jel ispravno, jer to

00:26:08.880 --> 00:26:10.880
isto može raditi i on i onda se tu

00:26:10.880 --> 00:26:12.880
u sukobu.

00:26:12.880 --> 00:26:14.880
Tako da zapravo to biti čovjek

00:26:14.880 --> 00:26:16.880
može se opet sveti samo na ono

00:26:16.880 --> 00:26:18.880
najosnovnije. Dobar dan,

00:26:18.880 --> 00:26:20.880
hvala,

00:26:20.880 --> 00:26:22.880
doviđenja. Koliko ljudi dođe

00:26:22.880 --> 00:26:24.880
u čan, ne kaže dobar dan,

00:26:24.880 --> 00:26:26.880
ne kaže hvala i ne kaže

00:26:26.880 --> 00:26:28.880
doviđenja. Znači ono,

00:26:28.880 --> 00:26:30.880
a toliko su sigurni u sebe,

00:26:30.880 --> 00:26:32.880
znači ono, toliko su

00:26:32.880 --> 00:26:34.880
kao ono,

00:26:34.880 --> 00:26:36.880
si bitni, a zapravo te neke

00:26:36.880 --> 00:26:38.880
osnovne stvari koje možda

00:26:38.880 --> 00:26:40.880
teta u dućanu ili neko

00:26:40.880 --> 00:26:42.880
sasvim deseti

00:26:42.880 --> 00:26:44.880
njemu može uljepša

00:26:44.880 --> 00:26:46.880
dan, a koliko je

00:26:46.880 --> 00:26:48.880
teško to zapravo reći iz nekog

00:26:48.880 --> 00:26:50.880
ega ili ne znam čega.

00:26:50.880 --> 00:26:52.880
To je kao ona bahatost,

00:26:52.880 --> 00:26:54.880
dođeš svaki put u restoran

00:26:54.880 --> 00:26:56.880
i očekuješ ono, da će biti

00:26:56.880 --> 00:26:58.880
jelo najbolje. Svaki put

00:26:58.880 --> 00:27:00.880
dođeš ono, kao znači

00:27:00.880 --> 00:27:02.880
očekuješ, imaš nekakve očekivanja.

00:27:02.880 --> 00:27:04.880
I onda dođeš jedan dan i onda

00:27:04.880 --> 00:27:06.880
te jelo razočara. I kaj onda?

00:27:06.880 --> 00:27:08.880
Češ se vratit?

00:27:08.880 --> 00:27:10.880
Hoćeš pitat da li nešto neštima?

00:27:10.880 --> 00:27:12.880
Hoćeš se žalit?

00:27:12.880 --> 00:27:14.880
Komunikacija je bitna.

00:27:14.880 --> 00:27:16.880
Jako ne, jer taj

00:27:16.880 --> 00:27:18.880
tvoj komentar, taj put u restoranu

00:27:18.880 --> 00:27:20.880
možda može njima dobro doć

00:27:20.880 --> 00:27:22.880
da skuže aha ok, možda smo

00:27:22.880 --> 00:27:24.880
malo stavili previše papra.

00:27:24.880 --> 00:27:26.880
Ili možda ono kao

00:27:26.880 --> 00:27:28.880
htjeli su te zavaljat,

00:27:28.880 --> 00:27:30.880
staviti neku drugu

00:27:30.880 --> 00:27:32.880
namirnicu, a naviko si na jednu.

00:27:32.880 --> 00:27:34.880
Pa onda kao

00:27:34.880 --> 00:27:36.880
davati do znanja da nešto neštima,

00:27:36.880 --> 00:27:38.880
komunicirat,

00:27:38.880 --> 00:27:40.880
davat dobru kritiku, davat lošu kritiku,

00:27:40.880 --> 00:27:42.880
to je super. To je onak

00:27:42.880 --> 00:27:44.880
vraća tebi, vraća ljudima

00:27:44.880 --> 00:27:46.880
kao ping pong.

00:27:46.880 --> 00:27:48.880
Ovo zapravo

00:27:48.880 --> 00:27:50.880
o čemu ti sad pričaš,

00:27:52.880 --> 00:27:54.880
kada razmišljam kroz prizmu vrhunskih

00:27:54.880 --> 00:27:56.880
sportaša, recimo prvaka u nečemu,

00:27:56.880 --> 00:27:58.880
to su ljudi koji često kažu da su

00:27:58.880 --> 00:28:00.880
zapravo samo se trudili

00:28:00.880 --> 00:28:02.880
usavršiti osnove.

00:28:02.880 --> 00:28:04.880
Pa isto tako i s ovim

00:28:04.880 --> 00:28:06.880
dobar dan, doviđenje itd.

00:28:06.880 --> 00:28:08.880
Čak i mojak čerko ima dvije godine prije

00:28:08.880 --> 00:28:10.880
nego što legne spati, tata joj čita

00:28:10.880 --> 00:28:12.880
knjigicu koja se zove

00:28:12.880 --> 00:28:14.880
Četiri čarobne riječi.

00:28:14.880 --> 00:28:16.880
Izvoli, molim, hvala.

00:28:16.880 --> 00:28:18.880
Sad sam zaboravio

00:28:18.880 --> 00:28:20.880
četvrtu. Izvoli, hvala,

00:28:20.880 --> 00:28:22.880
molim,

00:28:22.880 --> 00:28:24.880
sjetit ću se kasnije. Još ima jedna.

00:28:24.880 --> 00:28:26.880
Još ima jedna.

00:28:26.880 --> 00:28:28.880
Uglavnom to su osnove

00:28:28.880 --> 00:28:30.880
i nažalost

00:28:30.880 --> 00:28:32.880
pretpostavljam zato što smo svi mi

00:28:32.880 --> 00:28:34.880
nekako jako fokusirani

00:28:34.880 --> 00:28:36.880
na sebe.

00:28:36.880 --> 00:28:38.880
I onda kada si puno u svom svijetu koji se

00:28:38.880 --> 00:28:40.880
vrti oko tvojih interesa, oko tvojih ciljeva

00:28:40.880 --> 00:28:42.880
i tako dalje, zaboraviš da postoji drugi ljudi.

00:28:44.880 --> 00:28:46.880
I vjerujem

00:28:46.880 --> 00:28:48.880
da ove kvalitete

00:28:48.880 --> 00:28:50.880
koje si ti sada spomenuo su baš upravo

00:28:50.880 --> 00:28:52.880
kvalitete koje nam najviše trebaju danas

00:28:52.880 --> 00:28:54.880
u svijetu.

00:28:54.880 --> 00:28:56.880
Taj fokus zapravo, što je

00:28:56.880 --> 00:28:58.880
što je fokus?

00:28:58.880 --> 00:29:00.880
Možemo biti sebično fokusirani

00:29:00.880 --> 00:29:02.880
na sebe ili možemo

00:29:02.880 --> 00:29:04.880
biti fokusirani na... Oprosti je zadnja riječ.

00:29:04.880 --> 00:29:06.880
Oprosti je zadnja riječ.

00:29:06.880 --> 00:29:08.880
Oprosti je zadnja riječ.

00:29:08.880 --> 00:29:10.880
Možemo biti fokusirani na sebe,

00:29:10.880 --> 00:29:12.880
fokusirani na druge,

00:29:12.880 --> 00:29:14.880
fokusirani na overall cilj.

00:29:14.880 --> 00:29:16.880
U tom fokusu zapravo

00:29:16.880 --> 00:29:18.880
ono što je najveći challenge je

00:29:18.880 --> 00:29:20.880
naći isto mišljenike.

00:29:20.880 --> 00:29:22.880
To je

00:29:22.880 --> 00:29:24.880
nama u produkciji

00:29:24.880 --> 00:29:26.880
jako, jako teško naći.

00:29:26.880 --> 00:29:28.880
Ljude koji

00:29:28.880 --> 00:29:30.880
ne da briju kod mi,

00:29:30.880 --> 00:29:32.880
nego da naprosto

00:29:32.880 --> 00:29:34.880
da dijele tu istu viziju.

00:29:34.880 --> 00:29:36.880
A vizija nije

00:29:36.880 --> 00:29:38.880
i nikad nije bila nama

00:29:38.880 --> 00:29:40.880
vizija

00:29:40.880 --> 00:29:42.880
zaraditi. Reći kao ono

00:29:42.880 --> 00:29:44.880
e ja sad ovo radim samo zato da se

00:29:44.880 --> 00:29:46.880
obogatim. Mi nismo ušli u

00:29:46.880 --> 00:29:48.880
ovaj posao zato da se obogatimo.

00:29:48.880 --> 00:29:50.880
Jer onaj ko je

00:29:50.880 --> 00:29:52.880
tko god uđe u bilo koji biznis

00:29:52.880 --> 00:29:54.880
sa idejom da se

00:29:54.880 --> 00:29:56.880
obogati, već se radi

00:29:56.880 --> 00:29:58.880
mistake u prvim

00:29:58.880 --> 00:30:00.880
koracima. Ali

00:30:00.880 --> 00:30:02.880
taj fokus je to što

00:30:02.880 --> 00:30:04.880
te gura naprijed. Znači

00:30:04.880 --> 00:30:06.880
nađeš neke isto mišljenike,

00:30:06.880 --> 00:30:08.880
nađeš ljude s kojima

00:30:08.880 --> 00:30:10.880
možeš raditi, jer postoji ljudi s kojima ne možeš raditi.

00:30:10.880 --> 00:30:12.880
Isto kao što postoji ljudi s kojima

00:30:12.880 --> 00:30:14.880
ne možeš sjest na pivu, jer ti se naprosto

00:30:14.880 --> 00:30:16.880
ne sjeda s njima na pivu.

00:30:16.880 --> 00:30:18.880
I

00:30:18.880 --> 00:30:20.880
zaštiti taj fokus što je to točno

00:30:20.880 --> 00:30:22.880
za bilo koga, za tebe, za mene,

00:30:22.880 --> 00:30:24.880
za znaš ono,

00:30:24.880 --> 00:30:26.880
za ovih petero ljudi još u ovoj sobi koji su s nama,

00:30:26.880 --> 00:30:28.880
ovoga

00:30:28.880 --> 00:30:30.880
to je jako bitno.

00:30:30.880 --> 00:30:32.880
Često se sjetim one

00:30:32.880 --> 00:30:34.880
od hladnog piva, teško je

00:30:34.880 --> 00:30:36.880
full biti cool kad si tu.

00:30:36.880 --> 00:30:38.880
Ja imam osjećaj nekako da si ti to

00:30:38.880 --> 00:30:40.880
uspio.

00:30:40.880 --> 00:30:42.880
Pa mislim da je sad pravo vrijeme

00:30:42.880 --> 00:30:44.880
nakon pola sata našeg razgovora da možda

00:30:44.880 --> 00:30:46.880
kažeš ljudima s čime se točno

00:30:46.880 --> 00:30:48.880
danas sve baviš.

00:30:50.880 --> 00:30:52.880
Znači primarno

00:30:52.880 --> 00:30:54.880
sam redatelj

00:30:54.880 --> 00:30:56.880
ovoga i razvijam

00:30:56.880 --> 00:30:58.880
znači svoje projekte.

00:30:58.880 --> 00:31:00.880
Dokumentarni

00:31:00.880 --> 00:31:02.880
onda ne znam

00:31:02.880 --> 00:31:04.880
je li igrani, trenutno razvijam

00:31:04.880 --> 00:31:06.880
jedan dokumentažni film igrani, odnosno dva.

00:31:06.880 --> 00:31:08.880
Ali sad fokus je na jednom.

00:31:08.880 --> 00:31:10.880
I za taj film

00:31:10.880 --> 00:31:12.880
čekamo zapravo

00:31:12.880 --> 00:31:14.880
financiranje od Havca.

00:31:14.880 --> 00:31:16.880
Jako se veselim

00:31:16.880 --> 00:31:18.880
zapravo raditi taj film.

00:31:18.880 --> 00:31:20.880
Drugo,

00:31:20.880 --> 00:31:22.880
producent sam, znači vlasnik firme

00:31:22.880 --> 00:31:24.880
More Magnets

00:31:24.880 --> 00:31:26.880
koju imam sa partnericom

00:31:26.880 --> 00:31:28.880
u poslu

00:31:28.880 --> 00:31:30.880
s kojim sam

00:31:30.880 --> 00:31:32.880
započeo raditi taj

00:31:32.880 --> 00:31:34.880
business.

00:31:34.880 --> 00:31:36.880
Renata Lučić

00:31:36.880 --> 00:31:38.880
ona je isto redateljica.

00:31:38.880 --> 00:31:40.880
Ono po čemu smo mi možda

00:31:40.880 --> 00:31:42.880
specifičnije je

00:31:42.880 --> 00:31:44.880
to što smo redatelji jedan i drugi

00:31:44.880 --> 00:31:46.880
i plus imamo znači još

00:31:46.880 --> 00:31:48.880
ovoga produkciju svoju.

00:31:48.880 --> 00:31:50.880
To nije nešto što je često.

00:31:50.880 --> 00:31:52.880
Možda zato i produkciju gledamo malo drugačije

00:31:52.880 --> 00:31:54.880
nego

00:31:54.880 --> 00:31:56.880
producenti.

00:31:56.880 --> 00:31:58.880
Nemam pojma.

00:31:58.880 --> 00:32:00.880
Uglavnom ovoga, osim toga

00:32:00.880 --> 00:32:02.880
imam puno još interesa.

00:32:02.880 --> 00:32:04.880
Znači ono, teško je sad ono sve ili interese

00:32:04.880 --> 00:32:06.880
reći ono, s čim se baviš,

00:32:06.880 --> 00:32:08.880
što radiš, jer

00:32:08.880 --> 00:32:10.880
volim pisat.

00:32:10.880 --> 00:32:12.880
Što zapravo znači da volim pisat

00:32:12.880 --> 00:32:14.880
projekte svoje, volim

00:32:14.880 --> 00:32:16.880
grafiku, volim se nekako

00:32:16.880 --> 00:32:18.880
izražavati još grafički, odnosno

00:32:18.880 --> 00:32:20.880
kroz fotografiju.

00:32:20.880 --> 00:32:22.880
I u posljedno vrijeme to je fokus

00:32:22.880 --> 00:32:24.880
